<div class="com-share" data-id="12612" data-title="《麦浚龙联手黄伟文出新专辑，霸占了香港排行榜》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12612/medium/12612.jpg?1437760763" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12612.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
